\par\pard\plain \sa160\sb360\ql\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs24\b0\i1 Study Questions}
\par\pard\plain \tx360\li360\fi-360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 1.\tab Have you ever experienced a time when you were more focused on what God had provided for you in the past than on what He might have planned for you in the future?}
\par\pard\plain \li360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
