\par\pard\plain \tx360\li360\fi-360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 2.\tab In what ways does Abraham\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s willingness to sacrifice Isaac remind you of Christ\u8217\'92s sacrifice? In what ways are these sacrifices different?\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  Grigoni, M. R., Custis, M., Mangum, D., & Whitehead, M. M. (2012). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/csabraham?ref=Bible.Ge21.1-21&off=18372&ctx=ficance+in+Christ.%0a%0a~The+authors+of+the+n"}{\fldrslt\f2\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Abraham: Following God\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s Promise\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  (Ge 21:1\endash 22:24). Bellingham, WA: Lexham Press.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
