\par\pard\plain \tx360\li360\fi-360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 2.\tab Think of an instance where you witnessed God\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s deliverance in the midst of a struggle or trial. How did He deliver, and what did you learn about His character?}
