\par\pard\plain \tx360\li360\fi-360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 1.\tab How does the example of Abraham\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s faith encourage you in your walk with God? How does God\u8217\'92s faithfulness to His promise strengthen your faith?}
\par\pard\plain \li360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24
\par\pard\plain \tx360\li360\fi-360\sa160\sb180\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 2.\tab Read Hebrews 12:1\endash 3. How does the hostility Jesus endured affect your faith? How will remembering Christ\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s sacrifice help you in times of testing?}
